{"article_id":"tAjgbeKLAYeRGE7C","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Former Defense Secretary James Mattis poked fun at himself and President Trump at the 74th annual Alfred E. Smith Memorial Foundation Dinner in New York City on Thursday night , a day after the president called Mattis \" the world ' s most overrated general . \"","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"Mattis ,","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"who resigned last December","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"after clashing with Trump on the president 's Syria policy ,","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"said","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"he was honored by the `` overrated '' remark","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"because Trump \" also called Meryl Streep an overrated actress . '' `` So I guess","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"I 'm the Meryl Streep of generals , ''","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"Mattis joked ,","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"`` and frankly that sounds pretty good to me . ''","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"`` So I guess","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"I 'm the Meryl Streep of generals ,","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"and frankly that sounds pretty good to me . ''","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"- James Mattis , former defense secretary","depth":4},{"id":14,"text":"DEMS STORM OUT OF SYRIA MEETING WITH TRUMP :","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"'WE HAVE TO PRAY FOR HIS HEALTH '","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"Trump had fired back at Streep in January 2017","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"after she spoke out against him at the Golden Globe Awards .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"The Marine Corps four-star general 's name came up in a contentious White House meeting Wednesday about Trump ' s decision","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"to withdraw troops from Syria .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"A Democratic source familiar with the meeting told Fox News","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"that Senate Minority Leader Chuck Schumer , D-N.Y. , started to read the president a quote from Mattis from last Sunday :","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"`` And , in this case ,","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"if we do n't keep the pressure on ,","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"then ISIS will resurge .","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"It 's absolutely a given","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"that they will come back , ''","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"Mattis had said .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"That 's apparently when Trump cut Schumer off","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"and called Mattis overrated .","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"`` You know why ? ''","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"Trump said .","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"`` He wasn ' t tough enough .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"I captured ISIS .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"Mattis said","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"it would take two years .","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"I captured them in one month . ''","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"On Thursday night , Mattis also said","depth":5},{"id":38,"text":"that being called `` overrated '' by Trump didn ' t bother him","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"because he earned his \" spurs on the battlefield \"","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"and Trump \" earned his spurs in a letter from a doctor , \"","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"referring to Trump ' s medical deferments from serving in the Vietnam War due to bone spurs .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"\" I do stand before you ,","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"as was noted here ,","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"really having achieved greatness .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"I mean ,","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"I 'm not just an overrated general .","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"I am the greatest , the world 's most overrated , \"","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"Mattis said to laughter and applause .","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"The Al Smith Dinner is named for Alfred E. Smith ,","depth":3},{"id":50,"text":"who served as New York 's governor from 1923 to 1928","depth":4},{"id":51,"text":"and was the Democratic presidential nominee in 1928 ,","depth":5},{"id":52,"text":"losing to Republican Herbert Hoover of California .","depth":5},{"id":53,"text":"`` I am so excited to be here tonight .","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"I 'm happier than Hillary Clinton","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"watching CNN . ''","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"- Comedian Martin Short","depth":4},{"id":57,"text":"The event typically features a celebrity host","depth":4},{"id":58,"text":"-- and comedian Martin Short did the homors Thursday night .","depth":5},{"id":59,"text":"`` I am so excited to be here tonight , ''","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"Short told the crowd .","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"`` I 'm happier than Hillary Clinton","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"watching CNN . '' `","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"` Some of the most powerful people , elected officials , in America are here tonight , ''","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"Short said .","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"`` Plus Bill De Blasio . ''","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":131,"left":114,"right":130,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":79,"right":113,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":79,"left":0,"right":78,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":78,"left":77,"right":13,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":74,"right":76,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":74,"left":69,"right":73,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":69,"left":68,"right":4,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":68,"left":1,"right":67,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":67,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":5,"right":72,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":71,"right":9,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":70,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":76,"left":75,"right":12,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":113,